<plot>Cassie is an overweight woman who is trying to loose weight. Due to her family and friends persistence, she starts going to a dietitian. However she does not have enough will power to go through with her diet. Consequently, she decides to get a diet buddy,someone with whom she could share her weight problems. After meeting Luke, her new diet buddy, Cassie is going to realize that diets can be dangerous!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?600465</url></doc>
